sales of light commercial vehicles advance
after nearly two years ago , the market for light commercial vehicles beginning to see some light at the end of the tunnel .
the 9 425 vehicles registered in november in spain is an increase of 12.6 percent in 2008 and , more importantly , they represent the first increase after 22 consecutive months of decline , according to figures by the patronal manufacturers association anfac and ganvam , the dealers .
however , we need to balance the good news , as a reference for the comparison , the november 2008 , has been particularly bad , with a reduction of 60 % compared with the previous year .
as a result , despite last month 's events , the immatriculations accumulated during the 11 months are 40 percent less than those of the previous year .
since january , if we add all vehicles entering the category of light commercial vehicles - derived from cars , vans , pick-up fourgons light and light trucks with windows 95 853 have been sold .
high clouds that affect their request did not disappear . in fact , although they are bought by individuals , most of the purchases are made by small and medium enterprises , who pay in almost 100 % of the cases thanks to an external funding .
as more restrictions involved by limiting the credit , we must say other factors such as the rise in the unemployment rate and the continuation of the bad economic situation .
faced with this situation and difference for passenger cars , support for the purchase of the 2000e were used .
as well as individuals , independent and those who wish to acquire a light commercial vehicle up to 3.5 tons with a level of co2 emissions that does not exceed 160 grams per kilometer , can also benefit from it , but the number of operations speaks for itself .
yesterday , among ganvam recalled once again the need for the administration to pay special attention to these vehicles and industrial vehicles , trucks and buses .
the dealers ' association provides a 2010 similar to that ended , for which she is a fall in sales , from cars and the suv , of 19 % .
emergency aid to stop is now required
as has occurred with the system anti-lock restrictions abs and it will take place with stability control systems , esp , compulsory emergency aid to brake will form part of the european cars .
mandatory they are already on the newly licensed passenger cars and light commercial vehicles , while the rest of the vehicles , a period has been set up at the end of february 2011 .
the measure , imposed by the european union , is intended to strengthen the protection of pedestrians , even if in its course of action , it can also help prevent many blows back .
an assistant to the emergency brake is increasing pressure on the brakes in urgent cases detected by the system through shot in the foot of the driver .
but it has not always the pressure until the end .
according to a study by the manufacturer of car components bosch , one third of the drivers involved in accidents did not support the brakes before the collision , and half of them did not profit from its full force .
up to 1 100 accidents
the intervention of the assistance , revancha , requires maximum braking system , reducing the distance the car needs to stop .
according to a study by the eu , if all cars were with this type of points , up to 1 100 pedestrian accidents in which are involved could be prevented each year .
this reduction would be even more important with a popularisation emergency braking as intelligent systems : it is a sinister on four with the injured would be avoided .
in this case , the vehicle is equipped with a system that with a radar or a camera , detect obstacles and prevents the driver , slightly in addition to act on the brakes .
if the driver is , it applied by increasing the pressure on the assistance , if needed .
if it does not act , and that the collision is inevitable , it is the maximum effort on the brakes so as to minimize the damage .
