new tools for the expertise of cars
in these days of bad weather and accidents , garages cars are not the only winners .
every day , thousands of cars have suffered an accident are brought up in a garage , where an expert to assess the damage and the cost of repair .
each claim is different , and calculating the cost and time parts of workforce may be a long and complex process .
calculating compensation in hand the cost of between 20,000 and 30,000 euros , including spare parts and the workforce could take two or three hours .
on the other hand , with the assistance of the most recent computer tools , would be a matter of minutes .
it is for this reason that nearly 100 % of the experts use such systems .
service providers and solutions for the evaluation of claims and maintenance are dedicated to collecting information provided by manufacturers , and then to treat and to offer their customers in the form of a useful tool .
in spain , audatex , leader of the north american solera group , is the company ; 80 % of the estimates are carried out with its products .
other companies compete in the field assessment tools and the development of information about the sector are gtmotive and eurotax .
the work with the data provided by the manufacturers is far from easy .
according to audatex eduardo velázquez , director of trade , business in spain with 63 manufacturers and importers , and each one of them provides information in a different format .
in addition , the amount of data to treat continues to grow , so that over the past five years , more than versions , variables and motorisations were launched in the past 15 years .
when a new car fate on the market , these companies get down to work .
it is a very difficult work , because you need to catalogue every thousand pieces of the vehicle and put its price .
in addition it establishes a graphic image each model on which we can click on " intelligent " different parts of a car of tourism .
if it is a model sold heavily , the work could be ready in a week if the process is very quickly .
if it is a little car sold it can take three or four months . at present , audatex has full information on 99,2 % of the cars sold in spain .
among the most exclusive models , for example , they have information about the porsche , but not the ferrari and lamborghini .
on vehicles on the road , the figure is 99 percent .
for the job of documentation and preparing the databases , audatex has eight centers spread all over the world in spain , france , germany , the united states , brazil , mexico , china , and japan , and each of them is dedicated to some brands .
the national headquarters is located alcobendas in madrid .
here , more than 100 technicians or general experts on mechanical work simultaneously in three computer screens .
audatex invests 90 million every year to develop these databases .
data every month , 2.5 million are registered , and the customers are actualisations every two days .
drafting this huge flow of information allows companies to give them different customs and to offer a variety of products .
the most frequent application for repairs and maintenance , but in different countries , there are also tools for managing the theft or to calculate the value vénale or residual parts from a car .
the only company that has a guide making inquiries on the value of the used car eurotax in spain .
audatex does not propose in our country , but in the united states .
in view of the products offered by audatex , it is easy to get an idea of the type of support it can provide professionals in the sector .
this company provides 10 different tools , the flagship evaluation standard is audaplus , the solution of the fires , intended to experts .
there are cars , motorcycles and industrial light and heavy vehicles .
in addition to the cost of repair parts , it takes into account the time estimated by the manufacturer or fees of paint .
this tool comes according to its use of every estimate .
the higher cost of 5.75 euros , for customers who use it a little , the maximum 10 times per month .
then each insurance company , which makes thousands of expertise , its price negotiated with audatex .
other products , such as audavin , allow the full identification of a vehicle and equipment with which it is out of the assembly line , only thanks to its number of windows .
audaglass focuses on the glass of cars , and audasubastas is an open server at internet industry , which has enchérir on vehicles declared wrecks .
its statistics service is very useful to identify trends , conducting tests géo-démographiques or knowledge of the current problems by mark or model .
it is possible to study , for example , how many models of a determined went in the garage to mark a failure or how many have been serious claims for a given period .
gt behind is the only spanish company dedicated to the development of such tools .
it is selling , among other things , gt estimate , who is also intended to experts and provides digital images , as well as access to documents , official manufacturer price and time .
gt motivates is a business of the einsa group , founded in 1971 as a provider of services and solutions grim assessment , devoiture outages or maintenance .
the assessment guide gt is a historical reference product on the market .
the company is working with 24 thousand users in the garages , 3 100 experts and 53 insurance companies .
its business volume increased at a rate of 20 percent per year over the past three years , and it has been a turnover of 10,8 million in 2008 .
at the beginning of last year , it has begun the process of globalization , with the establishment of an office in paris .
from its side , audatex was born in germany in 1966 and has served spain in 1979 .
according to sources from the company , 62 percent of its turnover is done in europe and the rest of the world , and the remaining 38 % in north and south america and is working with 900 insurance companies and 33 , 000 , of which 3,000 are garages in spain .
the group 's global turnover solera - audatex , sidexa , informex abz , hollander and ims , the amount to $ 557 million , 3.3 % more than in 2008 .
in our country , the company will see 19.1 million , or 7.2 percent higher than last year .
