wrong estimate in four stages
with the auda-taller tool , the company audatex guarantees that the user gets an estimate only four steps : identifying the vehicle , seek spare room , to create an estimate and generate .
the ease of use is an essential element of these systems , especially in order to convince the older workers who , to a greater or lesser extent , are resistant to the use of new management techniques .
the database includes 1 034 vehicles , including 666 of tourism , 109 tout-terrains 137 motorcycles , 78 vans and 44 trucks .
naturally , to use a computer and connected to the internet are necessary .
once the model to repair identified thanks to the number of windows , a graphic image model in question is can you really necessary selects the room .
the user can include variables such as the price of the workforce , supplements or reduced , then he can give the estimate to get to the customer .
audataller is not a tool to estimate as audaplus , but a series of references .
the main difference between the two systems is that for the garages do not include the estimated time of workforce .
the cost to use this tool for the garage is 350 per year , which can be the subject of credit .
currently , the company audatex working so that these pictures are in three dimensions .
it is an innovation for engineers to see a very positive because it will , for example , to select a door and turn to see the internal front .
